Bug Report #3

Title: There's no feature for the buyer to check the shipping availability by PIN code on Shipping page
Environment: Production Environment
Severity: Medium
Priority: Medium
Assigned to: Developer
Reported by: Cary Peras
Reported on: 12/21/2021
Status: New
Pre-condition: User is in home page
Steps to reproduce: 
1. Choose an item to buy
2. Click "Add to card" 
3. Pop-up message displayed
4. Click "Proceed to checkout"
5. User is navigated to "Summary" page
6. Click "Proceed to checkout"
7. User is navigated to "Address" page
8. Click "Proceed to checkout"
Expected Result: According to the BRD, buyer must be able to check the shipping availability by PIN code on Shipping page
Actual Result: There's no feature for the buyer to check the shipping availability by PIN code on Shipping page
